name: Hear Me Out
description:
This is the Original Shirt that Started it all.. 
Started with just a logo and 
now you get to grab a soft tee 
for your own.

With the purchase of any of our product 
20% goes towards a 
relative charity to support
local Skateboarding and
 anything and everything that revolves around it. 
So that you the Consumer are 
now part of a community just by purchasing this T-shirt

These T-shirts are: 
100% cotton 
Machine Washable
